Study Hall: BUSINESS TAX BREAKS & INVESTMENTS with Wallstreet Trapper, Ms Business, & Quinetin Martin

In this study hall Ms Business breaks down how to save money on business taxes and best business practices. Wallstreet trapper and Quentin Martin joined us to talk about investing strategies and how to evaluate a company.
